#Commands# 

#The following commands use the trigger  !  as a example


Command       Syntax                     Explanation
 
Ban           !ban (nick)                Set's +b on the user's hostmask

Unban         !unban (nick)              Set's -b on the user's hostmask

Mute          !mute (nick)               Set's +b on the user's hostmask

Unmute        !unmute (nick)             Set's -b on the user's hostmask

Voice         !voice (nick)              Set's +v on the user

Devoice       !devoice (nick)            Set's -v on the user
 
Rehash        !rehash                    Rehash's the bot

Restart       !restart                   Restart's the bot

Op            !op (nick)                 Set's +o on the user

Deop          !deop (nick)               Set's -o on the user

Die           !Die

Ignore add    !ignore add (nick)         Add's the user's hostmask to the bot's ignore list

Ignore Del    !ignore del (nick)         Removes the user's hostmask from the bot's ignore list

Ignores       !ignores                   Shows you the bot's ignore list

Kick          !kick (nick)               Kicks the user off the channel

Kickban       !kickban (nick)            Kicks and set's +b on the user

Link          !link (bot)                Link's the bot to the specified bot

Unlink        !unlink (bot)              Unlink's the bot from the specified bot

Say           /msg (bot) !say (message)  Makes the bot say the specified message to the specified channel

Join          !join (channel)            Makes the bot join the specified channel

Part          !part (channel)            Makes the bot part the specified channel

Chanset       !chanset (option)          Set's the specifed option on the bot

Pubhelp       !pubhelp                   Makes the bot show you the PubCmd help list

Nick          !nick (new nick)           Changes the bot's nick to the specifed one

Mode          !mode (mode)               Set's channel modes that your specified

Calc          !calc (equasion)           Calculates the given equasion 

Fancy         !fancy (message)           Makes the given message colorful

Invite        !invite (user)             Invites the specified user

Cycle         !cycle (chan)              Cycles either the specified channel or if not specified, the current channel

#################################################################################################################################################################



